{
 "name": "RPlog_Dinner_and_a_wedding",
 "title": "Dinner and a Wedding",
 "summary": "At an intimate formal dinner party at the Casohav Lodge on snowbound Caspar, Interim Presav Thomas C. Mahon and Lynae Cassius gather a handful of close friends and comrades, then reveal that the evening's true purpose is their surprise wedding, to be conducted between the appetizer and the main course. Amid the skirling Caspian war pipes and Frederiko's incongruous jazz, Lynae presses the droid HM743 into service as best man and asks her best friend Maris and her newly revealed half-brother Sadim to stand with her. A weathered Chaplain weathers the good-natured chaos, restarting the ceremony once the wedding party is finally in place, and Mahon and Lynae exchange wry vows and rings before being pronounced husband and wife. Snarl nearly crushes the bride in a congratulatory hug while Enb'Zik looks on as the diplomatic witness, and the guests, HM743 and Sadim chief among them, plot mischievous decorations for the honeymoon ship. The scene closes with the couple wed and their friends already scheming, the marriage now firmly beyond any 'just kidding'.",
